  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../china-issues-annual-state-environment-report-ministry-calls-situation-very-grave">China Issues Annual ‚ÄúState of the Environment Report‚Äù - Ministry Calls Situation ‚ÄúVery Grave‚Äù</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-author-value">
          <label class="views-label-field-author-value">
        Posted by:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content">Deborah Seligsohn</span>
